{"tid":1179433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6月9日行程如下","createTime":"2019-05-31T06:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T08:40:38.000Z","uid":192358,"like":12,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ca6dd971617c1fe30a12957fc48e03b3326b04ec","tid":1179433,"uid":192358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"6月9日行程如下:<br />\n<br />\n瞓醒整野出門口，<br />\n午餐食個老麥（用支付寶）<br />\n去銅鑼灣遊行，順便打打卡，<br />\n行到累去時代廣場買杯喜茶解解渴，<br />\n行完散水，跟住就北上食海底撈，順便整甲，等我百度下邊度整甲平靚正先，<br />\n不過唔好太夜返屋企，<br />\n我仲要追極限挑戰同上淘寶買衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣既我開個wechat谷，大家約埋一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15063f071e3bca8d81783b6bb23ba1bb24b7d66a","tid":1179433,"uid":37458,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T06:14:47.000Z","msg":"既然上得去食海底撈 緊係去元朗買喜茶 <br />\n過關都快好多（中港牌）"},{"pid":"8561ac1c32b5a7bb1daa5506bdc9f4d9c7c38ea0","tid":1179433,"uid":192358,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15063f071e3bca8d81783b6bb23ba1bb24b7d66a","tid":1179433,"uid":37458,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T06:14:47.000Z","msg":"既然上得去食海底撈 緊係去元朗買喜茶 <br />\n過關都快好多（中港牌）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T06:18:21.000Z","msg":"都好喎，唔知有無邊位巴打有中港車呢，<br />\n咁就可以多d上去玩，我知道深圳有幾個商場同郊外景點好正，好想去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa05d1afd8c036efc8c0b3cbf858756b00840f6d","tid":1179433,"uid":192358,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T06:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人join?"},{"pid":"6900dbff338a57f67651c24e7e23391977deeca3","tid":1179433,"uid":170229,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T07:03:51.000Z","msg":"一早約咗fd 咗咁做<br />\n到時可能撞到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844c9e